items.text: We are the best pit shop in town. We give the best service, deliver the best quality, have the best professionals, and above everything else. WE LOVE WHAT WE DO!

STEVE’S PIT SHOP was established in 2001. We specialize in car maintainance, paint jobs, computerized wheel balancing, engine tuning, and interior decor of your beloved vehicle. What makes us diffferent from others, is that we treat your car, just the way we would treat ours.​

​We offer our clients a wide range of service options, and with the ability to handle upto 150 customers at a time, we are perfectly capable of tuning your car, customized to your needs, and ensuring your complete satisfaction. Once you bring your car to us and take it back, we guaratntee, that you will love the new experience.

We have specialists serving in every and all departments. Front Axles, Back Axles, Wheels, Crankshaft replacement and repair… All examples of stufff we do for our clients ad customers.

Once again, we look forward to welcoming you here!
